âš¡ Quick Start
With Docker:
bash

# 1. Copy all files
# 2. Navigate to folder
cd justice-client-portal

# 3. Start
docker-compose up -d

# 4. Open browser
http://localhost:3000

Without Docker:
bash

# 1. Copy all files
# 2. Install MySQL, create database
# 3. Navigate to folder
cd justice-client-portal

# 4. Install and run
npm install
npm start

# 5. Open browser
http://localhost:3000

